comments: Plumlee (DET) brushes Holmes' (SAC) hand as he attempts to control the loose ball and the contact is marginal.
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal contact to Grant's (DET) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Smith Jr. (DET) slightly extends his forearm into Bjelica's (SAC) body and does not dislodge him during the rebound.
Fox (SAC) cleanly blocks Smith Jr.'s (DET) shot attempt near the basket.
Barnes (SAC) places his arm to Grant's (DET) front at the start of his drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Smith Jr. (DET) and absorbs the contact.
Smith Jr. (DET) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Barnes (SAC).

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Jackson (DET) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Hield (SAC) grabs Jackson's shoulder as he attempts to gain leverage to get to the loose ball.
Bjelica (SAC) briefly grasps Grant's (DET) arm during the rebound.
Jackson (DET) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bjelica (SAC).
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Grant (DET).
Hield (SAC) slightly extends his arm into Bey's (DET) body during the screen and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Smith Jr. (DET).
Smith Jr. (DET) crosses over the plane of the free throw line before the ball makes contact with the rim.
Bey (DET) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Barnes (SAC) is in a legal guarding position with his arms vertical and he absorbs the contact from Grant (DET), who drifts forward during his jump shot attempt.
